                <h1>In legal limbo: DACA students reflect on a year of uncertainty</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/04ee638e-f364-47a1-abf0-90448c17882a.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Junior&#x20;Axel&#x20;Herrera&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Junior Axel Herrera</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                                                    
                <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/6a65bd6b-c78d-4b25-b736-aa96876ebeb5.sized-1000x1000.JPG?w=50&amp;h=50&amp;auto=format&amp;mask=ellipse&amp;fit=facearea&amp;facepad=2.5" class="author-image float-left pr-2" />
                                                        <div class="pt-1">
        
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/matthew-griffin">Matthew Griffin</a>
